title: Feel anxious when you don't have your cell phone? You may have 'nomophobia'—how to spot the signs
description: Nomophobia, short for "no mobile phone phobia," is a term used to describe the anxiety a person experiences when they don't have access to their mobile phone.

title: EU economics chief says Europe is gripped by a ‘double crisis’ — but it can avoid a recession
description: Europe can avoid a recession, Paolo Gentiloni, the European Commissioner for economic affairs, told CNBC on Saturday.

title: Many Italian parties are against China's Belt and Road Initiative, foreign minister says
description: Many Italian parties are against Rome's participation in China's Belt and Road Initiative, Antonio Tajani, the country's foreign minister said Saturday.

title: BMW unveils Vision Neue Klasse concept car as it touts the dawn of a new EV era
description: The first electric vehicles based on the Neue Klasse — or new class — architecture are set to enter production in 2025.
